2009 TAG TEAM LEAGUE IN FRONT OF A LIVE AUDIENCE

Combined HT:131"
Combined WT: 270lbs
Season Record:(0-1)

TEAM ICE
Hollie & Bella Rossi
Combined HT:132"
Combined WT: 305lbs
Season Record:(0-1)
Franchise record (3-2)

Welcome to Ultimate Surrender's 2009 Tag Team League.
The Pirates vs Team Ice. Four girls,
non-scripted, real tag team action.

This is the start of the new 2009 Tag Team Season. New teams; new wrestlers. The Beginning of what will be the the most brutal Tag Team Season yet!

In a stunning upset, the Pirates lost their first match up due to mismanagement of their tags. The Pirates cannot afford another defeat if they hope to make the playoffs.

Team Ice, is the biggest and strongest team in the league. No other team comes close to their combined weight. Hollie is a seasoned veteran, and Bella is this year's outstanding rookie. Can they pull together as a team and be a contender for the playoffs?

This is the fourth match of the new 2009 Tag Team season: 5 teams battle to see who will be crowned the Champion. If you have not joined yet, now is the time! This is the ground floor of the most brutal and sexiest wrestling league on the net.
title: LIVE TAG TEAM LEAGUE
